tracks.name: FTP
tracks.js_bw_compute: var computeFunction=function(){var file_requests = 10;var transactions_per_connection = 5 + 2 * file_requests;var delay = self.trackProperties()[1].value();var size_in_bits = self.trackProperties()[0].value() * 8;var user_tps_rate = self.trafficSettings().value() * 1000/delay * file_requests / transactions_per_connection;var raw_rate = ((size_in_bits * user_tps_rate) * 10);return raw_rate;};
